section.def:
licence
                (特許) means a licence granted under section
                7(1) or 8(1);

master
                (船長), in relation to a ship, includes any person
            (other than a pilot) for the time being in charge of the ship;

prohibited
                goods
                (禁制物品) means any arms and related material;

ship
                (船舶) includes every description of vessel used in
            navigation not propelled by oars;

subparagraph.content:
(if the ship is in the HKSAR) to cause the ship and any of its cargo to
                        remain in the HKSAR until the charterer, operator or master is notified by
                        an authorized officer that the ship and its cargo may depart;

paragraph.content:
either alone or accompanied and assisted by any person acting under his
                    authority, board the vehicle and search it and, for that purpose, use or
                    authorize the use of reasonable force;
